description-latin-dance-ar: argentina latin dance cup is the official qualifying round for the world latin dance cup, world latin dance cup 2024, and brings together the best dancers in each category of the salsa, bachata, tango and urban genres in the country. the best dancers in this competition win the right to represent our country at the France WLDC 2025 world championship in cartagena colombia from february 5 to 11.
description-latin-dance-la: los angeles latin dance cup is the official qualifier for the world latin dance cup 2024. it brings together the best dancers in each category of the country's salsa, bachata, tango, and urban dance genres. the best dancers in this competition win the right to represent our country in the world France WLDC 2025 in cartagena colombia from february 5 to 11. here you can find all the information related to the qualifying competitions that will take place in los angeles.
